</div></div><div class="sqs-block audio-block sqs-block-audio" data-block-type="41" id="block-yui_3_17_2_1_1631038235322_9289"><div class="sqs-block-content">



<div 
  class="sqs-audio-embed"
  data-url="https://static1.squarespace.com/static/5857604fbe6594376318ebbc/t/6138c94ec11a9111be6ed9e1/1631111516562/Abbot+Gregory+-+Dedication+of+the+Abbey+Church+9-7-21.mp3/original/Abbot+Gregory+-+Dedication+of+the+Abbey+Church+9-7-21.mp3"
